\c 9
\s Kusatenda kwevaJudha nekurashwa kwavo
\p
\v 1 Ndinotaura chokwadi muna Kristu, handinyepi, hana yangu ichindipupurira muMweya Mutsvene,
\v 2 kuti ndinoshushikana kwazvo neshungu dzisingaperi mumoyo mangu.
\v 3 Nekuti ndaishuva kuti ini ndomene ndipiwe rushambwa kuna Kristu nekuda kwehama dzangu, \add ivo\add* verudzi rwangu panyama;
\v 4 ndivo vaIsraeri vane kuitwa vana nekubwinya nesungano nekupiwa kwemurairo, neushumiri, nezvivimbiso;
\v 5 madzibaba ndeavo, naKristu wakabva kwavari panyama, \add iye\add* uri pamusoro pezvose, Mwari unokudzwa narinhi. Ameni.
\v 6 Kwete shoko raMwari serakakundikana. Nekuti havazi vaIsraeri vose vakabva kuvaIsraeri;
\v 7 Kana nekuti imbeu yaAbhurahamu, vose vana, asi \add zvinonzi\add*: Kuna Isaka ndiko kuchatumidzwa mbeu yako.
\v 8 Ndiko kuti: Avo vari vana venyama, ava havasi vana vaMwari; asi vana vechivimbiso vanoverengerwa kumbeu.
\v 9 Nekuti iri ishoko rechivimbiso \add rinoti\add*: Nenguva ino ndichauya, uye Sara uchava nemwanakomana.
\v 10 Handizvo chete; asi Ribhekawo wakati ava nemimba kune umwe, iye Isaka baba vedu;
\v 11 nekuti \add vana\add* vasati vaberekwa, kana kumboita chakanaka kana chakaipa kuti zano raMwari maererano nesananguro risimbiswe, kwete namabasa, asi naiye unodana,
\v 12 zvakanzi kwaari: Mukuru uchashumira mudoko,
\v 13 Sezvazvakanyorwa \add zvichinzi\add*: Jakobho ndakamuda, asi Esau ndakamuvenga.
\v 14 Zvino tichatiyi? Kusarurama \add kuriko\add* kuna Mwari here? Ngazvisadaro!
\v 15 Nekuti unoti kuna Mozisi: Ndichava nengoni kune wandichava nengoni naye, ndichava netsitsi kune wandinetsitsi naye.
\v 16 Naizvozvo zvino ha\add zvi\add*si zveunoda, kana unomhanya, asi zvaMwari unonzwira ngoni.
\v 17 Nekuti Rugwaro runoti kuna Farao: Ndizvozvi zvandakakumutsira, kuti ndiratidze simba rangu mauri, uye kuti zita rangu riparidzwe panyika yose.
\v 18 Naizvozvo unonzwira ngoni iye waanoda; uye unowomesa \add moyo\add* wewaanoda.
\v 19 Zvino iwe uchati kwandiri: Iye uchawanirei mhosva? Nekuti ndiani ungapikisa kuda kwake?
\v 20 Haiwa, asi iwe munhu ndiwe ani unokakavadzana naMwari? Ko chinhu chakaumbiwa chingati here kune wakaumba: Wandiitirei sezvizvi?
\v 21 Ko muumbi haana simba pamusoro pevhu here, kuti nebundu rimwe aite mudziyo umwe unokudzwa, neumwe unozvidzwa?
\v 22 Zvino kana Mwari achida kuratidza kutsamwa \add kwake\add*, nekuita kuti simba rake rizikamwe, atakura nemoyo murefu midziyo yekutsamwirwa yakagadzirirwa kuparadzwa;
\v 23 uye kuti azivise fuma yokubwinya kwake pamidziyo yengoni, yaakagara agadzirira kubwinya,
\v 24 yaakadanawo uye \add yatiri\add* isu, kusiri kuvaJudha chete, asi nekuvahedheni?
\v 25 Sezvaanorevawo kuna Hosiya \add achiti\add*: Vakange vasi vanhu vangu ndichavaidza vanhu vangu; naiye wakange asingadikamwi mudikamwa.
\v 26 Zvino zvichaitika \add kuti\add* panzvimbo pakanzi kwavari: Hamuzi vanhu vangu, ipapo vachaidzwa vana vaMwari mupenyu.
\v 27 Isaya unodanidzirawo maererano naIsraeri \add achiti\add*: Kunyange uwandu hwevana vaIsraeri hukaita sejecha regungwa, vakasara vachaponeswa;
\v 28 nekuti uchapedza basa nekugurisira mukururama nekuti basa rakagurisirwa richaitwa naMwari panyika.
\v 29 Sezvaakagara zvareva Isaya, \add achiti\add*: Kunze kwekuti Ishe wehondo atisiyira mbeu, tingadai takaitwa seSodhoma, takaitwa vakafanana neGomora.
\v 30 Zvino tichatiyi? Kuti vahedheni vasingatsvaki kururama, \add ndivo\add* vakawana kururama, iko kururama kwerutendo;
\v 31 asi Israeri achitsvakisisa murairo wekururama, haana kusvika pamurairo wekururama.
\v 32 Nei? Nekuti havana \add kutsvaka\add* nerutendo, asi nezvainge namabasa emurairo, nekuti vakagumburwa nebwe rinogumbura.
\v 33 Sezvazvakanyorwa, \add zvichinzi\add*: Tarira, ndinogadza paZiyoni ibwe rekugumbura, nedombo rekupinganidza; uye ani nani unotenda kwaari haanganyadziswi.
